nodes.title: 使用说明
widgets_values:
CHAOS 手绘风多幅 (Hand-drawn Art Multi-Ratio)
轻松将你的人物照片转换成极具艺术感的手绘插画风格，并自由选择7种经典画幅比例，创作独一无二的个性作品！

核心功能：
标志性手绘风格转换
采用精心调校的手绘插画风格 LORA 模型，一键赋予你的人物照片柔和细腻、富有表现力的绘画质感，仿佛出自专业画师之手。

7种画幅自由选
提供7种常用画幅比例方案，满足你在不同场景下的展示需求：

方案 0: 1:1（经典方形，适合社交媒体头像、帖子）

方案 1: 16:9（宽屏，适合视频封面、横向展示）

方案 2: 4:3（传统显示比例）

方案 3: 1:2（竖向长图，适合故事、部分移动端展示）

方案 4: 2:1（电影感宽幅）

方案 5: 3:4（竖向，适合人像特写、部分社交媒体）

方案 6: 9:16（竖屏，适合短视频、手机壁纸）

智能画布扩展
当你选择的画幅比例大于原始照片画布时，工作流会自动进行智能扩图，保持风格统一，画面自然延伸。

自定义图像高度
默认输出图像高度为1024像素（宽度根据所选画幅自动计算），你也可以根据需要自行调整此参数，以获得不同尺寸和清晰度的图片。

使用步骤：
上传照片：点击上传按钮，选择一张你想要转换的人物照片。建议使用清晰、光线良好的人物正面或半身照，以获得最佳效果。

选择画幅：从提供的7个画幅方案中，选择一个你最喜欢的比例（输入方案编号0-6）。

调整参数（可选）：如有需要，可以自定义图像生成高度。

点击运行：确认设置后，点击“运行”按钮。

等待生成：请稍作等待，CHAOS 手绘风多幅工作流将为你呈现一幅独具个性的艺术插画！

温馨提示与支持：
生成效果受原始照片质量、人物姿态和背景复杂度影响；

鼓励多尝试不同照片与画幅组合，挖掘更多风格变化；

我们持续优化模型与功能，敬请期待更多更新与惊喜！

如遇问题，欢迎进群免费咨询（QQ群：247228975）

nodes.title: Instructions for Use
widgets_values:
CHAOS Hand-Drawn Art Multi-Ratio
Effortlessly transform your portrait photos into beautifully stylized hand-drawn illustrations, and freely choose from 7 classic aspect ratios to create truly unique and personal artwork!

Core Features
Signature Hand-Drawn Style Conversion
Powered by a finely tuned hand-drawn illustration LORA model, your photo is instantly infused with soft, detailed, and expressive artistic qualities — as if drawn by a professional illustrator.

7 Flexible Aspect Ratio Options
Choose from 7 commonly used aspect ratios to suit different display and sharing scenarios:

Option 0: 1:1 – Classic square format, ideal for social media profile pictures or posts

Option 1: 16:9 – Widescreen, perfect for video covers and horizontal displays

Option 2: 4:3 – Traditional display format

Option 3: 1:2 – Vertical long format, great for stories or mobile-focused layouts

Option 4: 2:1 – Cinematic widescreen format

Option 5: 3:4 – Vertical portrait, suitable for close-ups and social platforms

Option 6: 9:16 – Full vertical screen, perfect for mobile wallpapers or short videos

Smart Canvas Expansion
If your chosen aspect ratio exceeds the original image dimensions, the workflow will automatically perform intelligent canvas extension — ensuring visual consistency and a natural composition.

Customizable Image Height
By default, images are generated with a height of 1024 pixels (width is auto-calculated based on aspect ratio). You may adjust this value to produce outputs of different sizes and resolutions.

How to Use
Upload Your Photo
Click the upload button and select a clear portrait or half-body photo with good lighting. For best results, use front-facing images.

Choose Aspect Ratio
Select your preferred aspect ratio from the 7 available options by entering the corresponding number (0–6).

Adjust Settings (Optional)
Customize the output image height if needed.

Click “Run”
Once settings are confirmed, click the Run button.

Wait for Rendering
Please wait a moment — the CHAOS Hand-Drawn Art Multi-Ratio workflow will generate your personalized, high-quality illustration.

Tips & Support
The final result may vary depending on photo quality, pose, and background complexity.

Try various photo and ratio combinations to explore different artistic effects.

We are continuously improving our models and features — stay tuned for exciting updates!

Need help? Join our support group for free assistance: QQ Group: 247228975
